description.narrative:
Financial sustainability : Effective fundraising at different levels (governmental, private sector and 
community) in order to increase access to water through RWH;
Institutional sustainability : Registration of SearNet as a legal entity.  
Environmental sustainability : RAIN and SEARNET will increase awareness on RWH at local, national and international levels to promote RWH as a significant complement to conventional systems of watermanagement;
Technical sustainability : Increase the capacity of local and regional RWH actors in order to facilitate implementation and knowledge concerning RWH projects.
Social sustainability : Exchange knowledge and expertise concerning RWH between the participants and members of their networks;
